---
title: Indian-Style Butter Chicken & Rice 2x the delicious portions!
description: Warm your heart (and belly) with our Indian-inspired butter chicken! You’ll sizzle chicken thighs with earthy garam masala and curry powder, then simmer in a buttery tomato sauce. Ladle it all over a bed of fluffy rice, then drizzle with yogurt and sprinkle with cilantro for a tangy-herbaceous finish, and serve with cheesy garlic pitas on the side.

This recipe is double the typical servings, providing 4 servings and 8 servings for a 2 person and 4 person box respectively.

